# QUICK REFERENCE

```bash
# Restore context
cat doc/agent/sketch.md

# Check history
git log --oneline -5 --show-notes

# Monitor training
tail -f logs/train.log

# View results
column -t -s $'\t' results.tsv

# Save implementation notes
git notes add -m "..." HEAD
```

